<headline>Special Weather Statement issued December 23 at 6:30AM EST  by NWS NorthernIndiana</headline>
<description>...Areas of fog may become locally dense...
Areas of fog are expected to develop this morning, initially mainly
west of Highway 31. The fog is likely to become dense later today with
visibilities occasionally dropping to one-quarter mile or less. If
you are traveling this morning, slow down and allow extra time to
reach your destination.</description>
